stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR

    [*] --> Created
    Created --> Pending : Configure & Activate

    Pending --> Triggered : Due Date Reached (System)
    Triggered --> Sent : Deliver Notification (System)
    Triggered --> Failed : Delivery Failure (System)
    Triggered --> Pending : User Reschedules
    Triggered --> Dismissed : User Dismisses / System Cancels

    Sent --> Acknowledged : User Views / Clicks
    Sent --> Overdue : Timeout / No Acknowledgment (System)
    Sent --> Pending : User Reschedules
    Sent --> Dismissed : User Dismisses

    Acknowledged --> Completed : User Marks Complete
    Acknowledged --> Overdue : Timeout / No Completion (System)
    Acknowledged --> Pending : User Reschedules
    Acknowledged --> Dismissed : User Dismisses

    Overdue --> Completed : User Marks Complete
    Overdue --> Pending : User Reschedules
    Overdue --> Dismissed : User Dismisses
    Overdue --> Archived : System Cleanup (No Resolution)

    Completed --> Archived : System Cleanup
    Dismissed --> Archived : System Cleanup
    Failed --> Archived : System Cleanup

    state "Legend" {
      direction LR
      _state1 : State
      _state2 --> _state3 : Transition (Actor)
    }